The __RESTBuilder__ (+v2.2.0) can create requests to different REST services.

```javascript
var instance = new RESTBuilder('https://api.yourdomain.com/users/');

// or
RESTBuilder.make(function(builder) {
    // builder === instance of RESTBuilder
    builder.url('https://api.yourdomain.com/users/create/');
    builder.post(self.body);
    builder.schema('User');
    builder.exec(function(err, response) {
        !err && response.$save();    
    });
});

```

__Default values__:

- RESTBuilder expects `JSON` response
- default method `GET`
- default timeout `10000` (10 seconds)
- default maxlength `unlimited`
- DNS resolver is enabled by default

